            any reason, but will usually do so only when fraudulent or incorrect results are reported by the
            organizer. Additionally, the VEKN reserves the right to invalidate any event reports not received
            within thirty days of the tournament date.
        </p>
        <h3 id="H9-5-event-status-updates">9.5. Event Status Updates
            <a class="link-secondary" rel="bookmark" href="#H9-5-event-status-updates">
                <i class="bi bi-link-45deg"></i>
            </a>
        </h3>
        <p>
            Tournament organizers and players may check on an event's reporting status by visiting the
            VEKN website. If an organizer's event appears as "Delinquent" or "Invalid" on this report two months in
