        </p>
        <h3 id="H9-7-tournament-reports-and-event-invitation-lists">9.7. Tournament Reports and Event Invitation Lists
            <a class="link-secondary" rel="bookmark" href="#H9-7-tournament-reports-and-event-invitation-lists">
                <i class="bi bi-link-45deg"></i>
            </a>
        </h3>
        <p>
            Tournament reports must be received by the deadlines specified in the Ratings Deadline and
