        </p>
        <h3 id="H9-8-non-open-vtes-events">9.8. Non-Open VTES Events
            <a class="link-secondary" rel="bookmark" href="#H9-8-non-open-vtes-events">
                <i class="bi bi-link-45deg"></i>
            </a>
        </h3>
        <p>
            Non-open VTES events are held in the following manner:
